Server Assistant Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 28/10/2023

Server Assistant ("We," "Us," "Our") is committed to protecting the privacy and security of your information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal and non-personal data when you use our Server Assistant services.

1. Information We Collect

1.1. User Data: We may collect personal information such as usernames, email addresses, and other identifiers provided by you or generated during your use of the Server Assistant.

1.2. Server Data: Our Server Assistant may collect and store data related to server usage, preferences, and interactions.

2. How We Use Your Information

We may use the information we collect for the following purposes:

2.1. Service Delivery: To provide the Server Assistant services, including task automation, command integration, and resource management.

2.2. User Communication: To communicate with you regarding your account, updates, and important information related to the service.

2.3. Security: To protect the integrity and security of your data and our services.

3. Information Sharing

We do not share your information with third parties except in the following circumstances:

3.1. Legal Compliance: When required by law, regulation, or legal process.

3.2. Protection of Rights: To protect our rights, privacy, safety, and security or the rights, privacy, safety, and security of others.

4. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

5. User Control

You may have the ability to review, update, or delete your account and personal information. Please contact us for assistance.

6. Third-Party Links

Our Server Assistant may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties.

7. Changes to Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting the updated Privacy Policy.

8. Contact Information

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@cryptodevservices.com.
